rows.label: bf05070100_0010
rows.name:
Amazing! The Cloud Sea
looks just like mountains.

rows.label: bf05070100_0030
rows.name:
Acedia is currently positioned
beyond the Cloud Ridge.

rows.label: bf05070100_0040
rows.name:
It would take quite some time to sail around,
so we'll be traveling over land from here.

rows.label: bf05070100_0050
rows.name:
Even a Divine Beast ship probably
couldn't cross that ridge.

rows.label: bf05070100_0060
rows.name:
So we have no choice but
to go overland, I guess.

rows.label: bf05070100_0090
rows.name: Rex, have you been here before?

rows.label: bf05070100_0110
rows.name:
My and Gramps's hometown. It's on
the other side of that ridge.

rows.label: bf05070100_0120
rows.name:
Huh, I wouldn't have pegged
you for a Liberalitan.
